tweet: @Captain_Jedi This opened the door for legislators to try to amend this bill, but those amendments failed. I did thank the legislature for at least making that change. But it doesn’t change the other issues clearly stated in my veto letter.

tweet: @Captain_Jedi They said only indemnification. At that point the choice is a ban that bankrupts schools and athletics or a ban that doesn’t. I chose the ban that doesn’t. If you notice, my call for the special session actually went beyond indemnification, adding “and related issues.” 2/

name: Spencer Cox
